For the 2007 film , see The Savages
Savages is a 2012 American crime thriller film directed by Oliver Stone .
It is based on the novel of the same name by Don Winslow .
The screenplay was written by Shane Salerno , Stone , and Winslow .
The film was released on July 6 , 2012 , and stars Taylor Kitsch , Blake Lively , Aaron Taylor-Johnson , Demian Bichir , Benicio del Toro , Salma Hayek , John Travolta and Emile Hirsch .